Subject: Re: [T2] racing buses on dirt

It's been done, at least one baywindow has run the Baja 1000.

However, buses are getting old enough that they are a bit too valuable to
hack.  You'd get a lot of component failures.  The weight distribution of
a bus isn't as good as a bug for serious off-roading.

George Lyle

